'''Imperial Exports''', later called '''Imperial/Republic''', was a modestly successful shipping company. In an effort to make their exports more profitable, they engineered a faster [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] route that made a stop off on [[Belsavis/Legends|Belsavis]]. Because the planet's atmosphere was unstable, IE was forced to create a consistently hospitable area on Belsavis for its ships to make berth. A huge dome was constructed over the [[Plawal Rift]] to provide a stable atmosphere. In order to fund this massive project, IE joined forces with [[Galactic Exotics]] in return for the exclusive rights to the planet's local fauna.

